title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Willard Outreach Faction
content:
The LSPD is undergoing a major rebrand. The new Willard Outreach Faction is the first-ever lowrider patrol car, upgradeable with hydraulics that’ll have you cruising neighborhoods like one of the cool kids … until you try to pull them over.

The Willard Outreach Faction can also be acquired from Warstock Cache & Carry if you’ve finished Slush Fund as a leader. Completing Slow and Low from Lowriders will unlock the Trade Price.
